main event: A UFO sighting involving three round white objects was reported, observed using ground radar and air intercept radar over a duration of 10 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 10 minutes, The objects appeared to be orbiting, They were observed disappearing and reappearing at a specific location, The coordinates of the sighting are 21.15N 170.15W, The report was considered unclassified and high reliability based on the observers.
witness description: Highly reliable naval officers observing the objects while shooting stars.
